* Enable Verbose\nAudit Logs
** What it adds
***_ notebook: runCommand (full code)
***_ jobs: runCommand
***_ databrickssql: commandSubmit
** How to enable
***_ Admin Settings → Advanced tab
***_ Toggle Verbose Audit Logs
***_ Configuration change is itself audited
** Security consideration
***_ Captures full command text
***_ May expose sensitive query parameters
***_ Review security policies for data exposure
** Use cases
***_ Full code execution auditing
***_ Compliance investigations
***_ Security incident forensics
@endmindmap
